          @Jamie_K Garcia lost an aerial duel. That is not an error. Zabaleta leaves Garcia to challenge which is the correct thing. Hart's positioning is wrong. Zabaleta has covered back reasonably well and is about to put Tosic under huge pressure when he lobs Hart. The ball is also bouncing and wouldn't have been easy to put away had Hart stayed on his line considering the direction Tosic was facing. Hart should have stayed on his line but had a rush of blood. As a result Tosic only has to hit the target over Hart to score. It's harsh and it happened in a flash but I agree with whoscored.
